text:
Cook's six TDs lift Union County past Saints in wide-open shootout 
Sat, Oct 24, 2015 @ 12:18 am 
The Times-Union 
UNION COUNTY 60 
CEDAR CREEK CHR. 52 
Ty Cook threw for five TDs and ran for a sixth as the Fightinâ€™ Tigers held on for a wild victory over the visiting Saints (5-3). ... Franklin Williams and Dairon Alexander returned interceptions for touchdowns for Union County (7-1), which nearly blew a 23-point lead. ... Cedar Creek Christian quarterback Ivory Durham threw five touchdown passes, four of them to Tron McCarter.
